## Spacelift Migration Notes

Spacelift was detected as enabled before this PR. The generated mixin sets
`settings.spacelift.workspace_enabled: false` via deep merge. Existing Spacelift state is
**not** migrated — if you want to run Atmos Pro and Spacelift in parallel, revert the
`workspace_enabled: false` override in the mixin and run both.
